{"tid":1094753,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"蒼井空食三人份量 激重42磅 最新照","createTime":"2019-04-06T14:06:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-06T18:53:14.000Z","uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"d6c1e048d818f0d29f35cb0ef59b5daf5df2d019","tid":1094753,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T14:06:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190406/large/1554537648_6f2d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190406%2Flarge%2F1554537648_6f2d.jpg&h=f273ba10&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n日本前AV女優蒼井空為丈夫DJ NON正懷雙胞胎，其預產期是今個月，她早前透露肚子已經很大很重，每次外出都不容易，沖涼時見到自己的身體也會很驚訝。蒼井空今日又再更新網誌及微博，自言心情十分緊張及感不適，連日來亦有上載近照，臨盆在即的蒼老師明顯加大幾個碼，她也自爆懷孕至今已重了19公斤（即近42磅），她在微博自言：「沒辦法我要吃三個人的飯。」雖然重磅了不少，但仍有網民大讚她是「童顏媽媽」。<br />\n<br />\n至於跟蒼井空同期吃香AV界、惠比壽麝香葡萄昔日好姊妹麻美由真、吉澤明步、Mihiro（朝美穗香）、希志愛野、西野翔等，近日就相約賞櫻，正所謂十年人事幾番新，眾女星已相繼從良，西野翔更留言：「已經畢業6年，感謝多年來的友情，真的很愛各位。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190406/large/1554537664_7985.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190406%2Flarge%2F1554537664_7985.jpg&h=0c94bc85&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n成班肉便器<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190406/large/1554537648_bc40.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190406%2Flarge%2F1554537648_bc40.jpg&h=7e4b5b44&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果下一刻係拍片就正"},{"pid":"a7114d092d60056104091100e35d1316f4ca5531","tid":1094753,"uid":116131,"like":7,"dislike":3,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T14:12:54.000Z","msg":"人地肉便器都唔到你屌啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11b78e57b1cb5cac10debe8dd2afaa85ff884a72","tid":1094753,"uid":4942,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T18:42:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190406/large/1554537664_7985.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190406%2Flarge%2F1554537664_7985.jpg&h=0c94bc85&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n正撚到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d82c7d71e82c562ea74829aef6cd7994ca6d3a44","tid":1094753,"uid":23236,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T18:47:28.000Z","msg":"小公主"},{"pid":"e82859055e76e1fb502cd292bf5fcc46fdd22d61","tid":1094753,"uid":55924,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T18:48:57.000Z","msg":"我初次射精就係比左佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"282cfe79a52d329f9ce0de0af0aaa3b54dbe81ed","tid":1094753,"uid":16846,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T18:53:14.000Z","msg":"咪撚咁口臭啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}